Hello,

I am creating a module in which i want to check if my personalization token is empty.
personalization token is {{personalization_token("contact.firstname", " ")}} .

If personalization token has value, i want to display "Hello, Contact.firstname"

If the personalization token is empty, i want to display a new html text section.

So far i have this code, would appreciate some help on where i need to modify it for it to work.

{% set Value = personalization_token("contact.firstname","Null") %}
{% set NewValue = Value %}
{% if NewValue == "Null" %}
&lt;p&gt;
Glad to have you with us!
&lt;/p&gt;
{% elif %}
&lt;p&gt;
Hello, {{personalization_token('contact.firstname', ' ') }}
&lt;/p&gt;

{% endif %}
